{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/3-dicas-para-voc√™-usar-em-projetos-react-typescript/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://devjuniorplus.com.br"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/3-dicas-para-voc√™-usar-em-projetos-react-typescript/"},"frontmatter":{"description":"Aprenda a usar essas features do Typescript!","title":"3 dicas para voc√™ usar em projetos React + Typescript! ","date":"04 de mar√ßo de 2022","image":"assets/images/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpeg"},"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Hong Kong\"\n        title=\"Image from Chi Lok TSANG - Unsplash\"\n        data-src=\"/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/18e3b/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/46946/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg 240w,\n/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/55489/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg 480w,\n/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/18e3b/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg 960w,\n/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/60e21/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg 1440w,\n/static/16464d65f8a8c21df51bc4311fbf8ea2/69b48/chi-lok-tsang-koxxmfunspa-unsplash.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Introdu√ß√£o</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Antes de mais nada, se voc√™ est√° aprendendo sobre React + Typescript, fiz um v√≠deo que ficou bem massa, depois da uma olhada l√°. üòé </p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/A4wImDtQw7w\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</ br>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Hoje vamos abordar uma dica r√°pida por√©m muito √∫til no dia-a-dia como Dev se voc√™ utiliza Typescript: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pick </li>\n<li>Omit</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Bora aprender a usar na pr√°tica com exemplos da vida real?! </p>\n<h2>Pick</h2>\n<p>Veja o exemplo abaixo: </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/Modal/index.tsx</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tipagem do componente Modal</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ModalProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  isOpen<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  size<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'small'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'xsmall'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'medium'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'large'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  children<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ReactNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onRequestClose</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Componente Modal</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Modal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  isOpen<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'medium'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  children<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  onRequestClose\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n \n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  \t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">S.Container</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">size</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* a propriedade `size` √© passada para o Container */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    \t\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">S.Container</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Nesse exemplo, vamos usar React + Styled Components</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Criamos um <code class=\"language-text\">type</code> para um componente de <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code>, agora vamos estilizar usando o <a href=\"https://styled-components.com/\">Styled Components</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/Modal/styles.ts</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> css <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'styled-components'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \"Pegamos\" apenas a propriedade `size` de `ModalProps`</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Pick<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'size'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Passamos a tipagem para o component Container</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Container <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ContainerProps<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> size <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> css<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\"> // Recebe props e desestrutura, pegando o </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>size<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>size <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'small'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Verifica se o `size` √© igual \"small\" e aplica uma estiliza√ß√£o</span>\n    css<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n      width: 26rem;\n      height: 80%;\n    </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> </code></pre></div>\n<p>Ou seja, aproveitamos a tipagem para do componente <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code> e utilizamos apenas uma propriedade do <code class=\"language-text\">ModalProps</code> para nosso componente estilizado <code class=\"language-text\">Container</code>.</p>\n<p>Nesse caso poder√≠amos criar uma nova tipagem apenas para o <code class=\"language-text\">Container</code>, n√£o teria problema. </p>\n<p><strong>Mas a vantagem em utilizar Pick nesse caso √© que, como a propriedade <code class=\"language-text\">size</code> recebe apenas algumas op√ß√µes, se alterarmos no <code class=\"language-text\">ModalProps</code> automaticamente alteramos no <code class=\"language-text\">ContainerProps</code>.</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/Modal/index.tsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ModalProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  isOpen<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  size<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'medium'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'large'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// -> Perceba que `size` agora s√≥ aceita duas op√ß√µes</span>\n  children<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ReactNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onRequestClose</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/Modal/styles.ts</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Pick<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'size'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// -> Nao precisamos mexer em nada aqui, o `size` vai aceitar apenas 'medium' ou 'large'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Com o <code class=\"language-text\">Pick</code> podemos selecionar mais de uma propriedade de um tipo:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Pick<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'size'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'title'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Podemos selecionar quantas propriedades quisermos</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Mesmo que fazer: </span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  size<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'small'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'xsmall'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'medium'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'large'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Omit</h2>\n<p>O <code class=\"language-text\">Omit</code> √© bem parecido com o <code class=\"language-text\">Pick</code>, por√©m ao inv√©s de selecionar uma propriedade de uma tipagem, ele remove (omite).</p>\n<p>Exemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ModalProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  isOpen<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  size<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'small'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'xsmall'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'medium'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'large'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  children<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ReactNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onRequestClose</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Omit<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'title'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// O mesmo que fazer:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\ttype ContainerProps = { -> Todas as propriedades menos a `title`</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t\tisOpen: boolean;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \t\tsize?: 'small' | 'xsmall' | 'medium' | 'large';</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \t\tchildren: React.ReactNode;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \t\tonRequestClose: () => void;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t};</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>E assim como o <code class=\"language-text\">Pick\u001b</code>, podemos remover uma ou v√°rias propriedades de uma tipagem.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContainerProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Omit<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ModalProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'title'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'isOpen'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token string\">'size'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// O mesmo que fazer:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\ttype ContainerProps = { -> Todas as propriedades menos a `title`, `isOpen` e `size`</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \t\tchildren: React.ReactNode;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \t\tonRequestClose: () => void;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//\t};</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Massa n√©?!</p>\n<h2>Dica b√¥nus</h2>\n<p>Se voc√™ utiliza a lib <a href=\"https://react-select.com/home\">react-select</a> com valida√ß√£o utilizando o <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/yup\">Yup</a>, podemos fazer o seguinte para melhorar nossa valida√ß√£o:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Valida√ß√£o com React-Select + Yup</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> schema <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Yup<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Yup<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">required</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Campo obrigat√≥rio\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Passamos como objeto, por causa do react-select</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Tipagem para User</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UserProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  password<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tipagem para um formul√°rio de Adi√ß√£o</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SubmitDataProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    value<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> Omit<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>UserProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'id'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Exemplo de formul√°rio utilizando <strong>React Select</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Form</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onSubmit</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleSubmitData<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Select</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Selecione um usu√°rio<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">options</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>usersoptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    \n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Button</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Adicionar</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Button</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Form</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Quando um usu√°rio √© selecionado e o formul√°rio √© submetido, o <strong>React Select</strong> envia como:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    value<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// usuario com id 1 por exemplo</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Agora basta criar um objeto para enviar na chamada √† API:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handleSubmitData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> SubmitDataProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>rest <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  \n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> dataSubmit <span class=\"token opera